1 vehicle dismantling businesses located outside of and within six miles of the boundaries of the city
2 unless the county governing body in which the area is located has adopted regulations under this
3 section that are applicable in the area.
4 “(5) Before granting approval for a supplemental dismantler certificate, the governing body of
5 a city or county shall notify all property owners that are or that will be adjacent to the motor ve-
6 hicle dismantling business once the business moves, expands or opens an additional place of busi-
7 ness.
